+\fBxdg-mime\fR(1),
+\m[blue]\fBMIME applications associations specification\fR\m[]\&\s-2\u[1]\d\s+2,
+\m[blue]\fBRFC 6068 \- The \*(Aqmailto\*(Aq URI Scheme\fR\m[]\&\s-2\u[2]\d\s+2
+.SH "EXAMPLES"
