+.PP
+\fB1\fR
+.RS 4
+Error in command line syntax\&.
+.RE
+.PP
+\fB3\fR
+.RS 4
+A required tool could not be found\&.
+.RE
+.PP
+\fB4\fR
+.RS 4
+The action failed\&.
+.RE
+.SH "EXAMPLES"
